data.description: Live in one unit while your tenant helps pay your mortgage as you build equity in your own home! Over/ Under 2 Family in the Great Northern Part of Newark. Updated Kitchen and Baths. Brand new separate furnaces and hot water heaters. Front gate opens up for a possible parking spot! Just across the river from Kearny and Harrison, great location for commuters. Close to schools and shopping!
